RACE.FOOTNOTES: CHOOSEN ONE away very well almost clearing field in first to jumps, kept to task in a mild drive while winning comfortably. RACY SWEET CORONA bumped solidly at the start by outside rival, accelerated well and kept to task under a hand drive in a promising debut. FANCY POLLITICS broke in, asked left handed throughout in an even effort. JAMAICA LIGHTS broke a bit slow, came in and bumped rival at the start, hand ridden first half of the race, asked late and responded well. MR FAVORITE JESS away cleanly, asked right handed immediately, did not fully level till late in an even effort. SNEAKY KID fractious in the gate, ducked in and bumped rival at the start, ridden cautiously rest of the way while in tight. FAMOUS TRESSY tossed head, came away slow and pushed in by outside rival at the start, asked right handed early, lacked path and ridden to wire. BEDUINOS FAVORITE fractious in post parade, stayed in gate and completely missed the break and lost all chance.
